Permisos

Octal Notation (permisos)	
	
chmod +	
	
7 (read,write,execute)	
6 (r,w)	
5 (r,e)	
4 (r)	
3 (w,e)	
2 (w)	
1 (e)	
0 (none)	

	
Permisos básicos en Linux (CHMOD)	
– – – – – – – – –	0
r——–		400
r—r–r–		444
rw——		600
rw-r–r–		644
rw-rw-rw-	666
rwx——		700
rwxr-x—		750
rwxr-xr-x	755
rwxrwxrwx	777
